Category:Sith Lords of the reconstituted Sith Empire

nodes.text: Servant Eleven was a Sith Pureblood female Sith Lord of the reconstituted Sith Empire during the Cold War. She was an Emperor's Hand, the most trusted servants of the Sith Emperor, alongside her colleagues. On Corellia, she worked with the Emperor's Wrath in order to protect Darth Vowrawn from Darth Baras' assassins.
